Package com.fhkiel.oopproject.container

Class CharacterContainer

java.lang.Object
com.fhkiel.oopproject.container.CharacterContainer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CharacterContainer extends Object implements Serializable
Class-Description:
Container for created characters with basic CRUD functionality Implemented as singleton and Serializable to save the data on a hard drive.
